snippet.title: Elf Bowling - Bocce Style! (Windows game 2004)
snippet.description:
Elf Bowling - Bocce Style! is a freeware game.
The object of the game is that you have to kick a penguin and elf farther than opponent player.
But if the object reach the end line, it will disappear.
